\id TIT - Matumbi Bible Version
\h Tito
\toc1 Balua ya Pauli kwa Tito
\toc2 Tito
\toc3 Tit
\mt1 Tito
\mt2 Balua ya Pauli kwa Tito
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Balua yi' niandike nenga na Pauli, ntumisi wa Nnu'ngu' na ntumilwe wa Yesu Kilisitu. Nitumilwe kwa kitumbu sa kwayi'gana bandu babasaulilwe na Nnu'ngu' li'nga bapate kumwu'bi'lya no tanga ukakape waulu'a kwalongoya tama maisa magolou,
\v 2 na kwapeya mau'bi'lyo go li'nda ukoto wangayomoka. Nnu'ngu', ywangali longela ubu'su', aalagi ukoto wo kubile balo ata umbilwa kwa dunia.
\v 3 Lakini, munsimu wake Nnu'ngu' aumukwi liyi'gi'yo lyake. Naakamukiyilwe nwaya liyi'gi'yo lyo na Nnu'ngu', Nkosopoli witu.
\p 
\v 4 Nikuandikya wa Tito, wamwana wangu' wa kakape muimani yatuiu'bi'lya. Nikulu'bya ngu'ngu' na amani bu'ka kwa Nnu'ngu' Tati' na Kilisitu Yesu, Nkosopoli witu.
\s1 Lyengo lya Tito ku Kilete
\p 
\v 5 Naakulei kunni'ma wa Kilete li'nga ubi'ke wiso makowe gagaaigile, pamope no sawa api'ndo ba kanisa kwa kila kilambo, kati mu'lu' mwanaakulagile.
\v 6 Mpi'ndo wa kanisa apalikwa kaneabe na lukoolo na mundu, abe nnalu'me wa nnwawa yumo. Bana bake bapalikwa babe babau'bi'lile bangali sitakilwa kwa makowe ga umbu'ku'su' wala kotoka yu'wa.
\v 7 Nnyi'mi'li'ki wa kanisa apalikwa panga mundu ywangali bi'ki'lwa lukoolo kwa mwanjaa akamukiyilwe lyengo lya Nnu'ngu'. Kwa nyo kaneabe mundu ywakwipuna, ywayu'ngu'ya usika, nnobya wi'mbi', mwene nnomo wala pala mbanje kwa ndi'la ndau.
\v 8 Ila abe mundu ywapenda kwapokya ageni wiso, ywapenda panga makowe manogau, mwene ikima, mwene aki, mpeleteu na ywawesa kwiyi'mi'li'ka mwene.
\v 9 Apalikwa kamwa Liyi'gi'yo lya kakape kati mwaliyi'ganilwa, li'nga awese kwakangamaya bi'ngi' kwa mayi'gano ga kakape na kwakalipya balu' babagataukya mayi'gano ago.
\p 
\v 10 Kwa mwanjaa babile bandu baingi, muno balu' babau'bi'lile bu'ka mudini ya Kiyahudi, bembe bayu'wali na baaobeya bi'ngi' kwa mayi'gi'yo ga kilalo.
\v 11 Bapalikwa bakanikiyilwe, kwa mwanjaa baaobeya bandu bu'ka nsengo gumo ata wi'ngi' kwo yi'gana mayi'gi'yo gangali palikwa li'nga bapate mali kwa ndi'la ya ukongi.
\v 12 Kwaabile na nnondoli yumo ywabe Nkilete ywaabaite panga,
\q1 “Akilete masu'ba goti abu'su',
\q2 bapwaikali kati inyama ya mmwitu,
\q1 bapendi mila muno
\q2 lakini bapendili panga kasi!”
\p 
\v 13 Ukong'ondeli wu'no wa kakape. Kwa nyo wakwi'li'ke kwa ukali' li'nga bapate baa na imani yaitimile.
\v 14 Bakotoke pi'kania u'mo ya Kiyahudi yangali maana yoyoti, na malagyo ga bandu babaukana ukakape.
\v 15 Kwa balu' bababile na mwoyo nnogau, kila kili'be kwabe kipeleteu. Lakini ntu'pu' sosoti sakipanga kipeleteu kwa bandu asapu na bangali u'bi'lya Nnu'ngu', kwa mwanjaa malango na myoyo yabe itwi'li usapu.
\v 16 Bembe babaya panga bantangite Nnu'ngu', lakini iyendo yabe ilaya mpu'la panga bendakunkana. Baatisukilwa, bangali yu'wa, na bangali pwaika mulikowe lyolyoti li'lu' linogau.
\c 2
\s1 Mayi'gano ga kakape
\p 
\v 1 Lakini wenga wa Tito, upalikwa kwayi'gana bandu mayi'gano ga kakape.
\v 2 Waabakiye analu'me agoi bapange makowe kwo li'ngi'lya, babe na isima na bawese kwitawala bene. Kai', babe ba kakape muimani, muupendo na muukomeyi.
\p 
\v 3 Nyinyonyo waayi'gane alwawa agoi batame mumaisa mapeleteu. Kanebabe abai au babalobya, ila babe bandu bo yi'gana mayi'gi'yo manogau.
\v 4 Kwo panga nyo, babe kabaayi'gana alwawa ai'nja kwapenda asengo babe na bana babe,
\v 5 babe bandu babawesa kwitawala bene, apeleteu, babatunja wiso misengo yabe, anogau, babaayu'wa asengo babe, li'nga mundu ywoywoti aakane kulisalawa liyi'gi'yo lya Nnu'ngu'.
\p 
\v 6 Nyinyonyo waakong'ondeli na ansembe babe bandu babawesa kwitawala bene.
\v 7 Nawenga mumakowe gako goti upalikwa ulaye iyendo nogau li'nga uyigilwe, na kwo laya ukakape na isima mumayi'gano gako,
\v 8 no longela wisowiso pangali bi'ki'lwa lukoolo, li'nga babakutaukya bapate isika. Kwa nyo baapanga ntu'pu' likowe lyo longela lyalibile lyakau kwitu twenga.
\p 
\v 9 Waayi'gane abanda baayu'we angwana babe mumakowe goti, baapulaise na kanebataukane nabo,
\v 10 wala kanebayibe, ila balaye panga au'bi'li'ka, li'nga lyengo lyabe lyoti lyaapange bi'ngi' bautilwe na mayi'gano ga Nnu'ngu' Nkosopoli witu.
\v 11 Kwa mwanjaa ngu'ngu' ya Nnu'ngu' yaileta ukosopoli kwa bandu boti ibonekine.
\v 12 Ngu'ngu' yo ituyi'gana kana ulau na maminyikio ga dunia, li'nga tupate tama mumaisa ga kwitawala, ga aki, na mapeleteu munsimu wu'no,
\v 13 ku'no katulolela lisu'ba lyaliyaliwite lyatuliu'bi'lya, nsimu wawapitya utukupu wa Nnu'ngu' Nku'lu' na Nkosopoli witu Yesu Kilisitu.
\v 14 Ywembe aipiyite kwa kitumbu situ li'nga atuli'pi leni lya masambi goti na kutupanga twabandu apeleteu bake, bandu bene kilu'lu' so panga makowe manogau.
\p 
\v 15 Bai, wayi'gane mayi'gi'yo ga, wakong'ondeli bandu na wakalipi kwa makakala goti. Mundu ywoywoti kaneakusalawe.
\c 3
\s1 Maisa ga Kikilisitu
\p 
\v 1 Waaku'mbu'ki'ye bandu panga bapalikwa kwaisimu na kwayu'wa alongosi babaatawala. Mwibi'ke wiso kwa kila lyengo linogau.
\v 2 Waabakiye kanebantukane mundu ywoywoti, kanebayu'mane, ila babe anogau na atu'lya kwa bandu boti.
\v 3 Kwa mwanjaa twenga twabene nsimu nsi'si' twaabile twaalalo, twakingayu'wa, twaatikongelwa, na twaatabilwe na maminyikio ga kila sampuli. Twaatami muulau na bwigu, twaatisukilwa na twenga ngatusukwana twabene na bene.
\v 4 Lakini unogau na upendo wa Nnu'ngu', Nkosopoli witu pawaumukulilwe,
\v 5 aatukosopoli lili kwo pi'tya makowe gitu ga aki gatupangite, ila kwa kiya sake. Aatukosopoli kwa kutupeletea kwo belekwa kai' na kutupanga twayambi' kwa ndi'la ya Loo Mpeleteu.
\v 6 Nnu'ngu' atuulukiye Loo wake pangali li'ngi'lya kwo pi'tya Yesu Kilisitu Nkosopoli witu,
\v 7 li'nga tubalangilwe aki kwa ngu'ngu' yake, tupate panga twaalisi ku'no katuu'bi'lya tubile na ukoto wangayomoka.
\p 
\v 8 Mayi'gi'yo gano ga kakape. Nikupala wenga ugakong'ondeli makowe ga, li'nga boti babamwu'bi'lya Nnu'ngu' babe na kilu'lu' so panga makowe manogau. Mayi'gi'yo go manogau kai' gakumpwaika kila mundu.
\v 9 Lakini utame kuutalu na nnomo au mataukyano ga kilogeloge bu'kana na salya au ngolo. Ago goti gapwaikali, kai', gabule bai.
\v 10 Mundu ywayu'mania bandu, unkwi'li'ke mala yimo au ata mala ibi'li', mana aakana kukuyu'wa ulekane nakwe mpamo.
\v 11 Utangite panga mundu kati ywo aulei ukakape, na sambi yake impwatya mwene.
\s1 Mayi'gi'yo ga kuundi'la
\p 
\v 12 Nibini yenda tama kukilambo sa Nikapoli kwa wu'no nsimu woti wa mbepo, lakini naalu'a kuntuma Atema au Tikiko kasako, mana aikite akwo wenga waabini isa Nikapoli li'nga tukwembane.
\v 13 Ukondamie kunnyangatia Zena yu'lu' mundu wa salya, na Apolo. Waapei ili'be yoti yaipalikwa mumwanja wabe.
\v 14 Ayi' nga ndi'la yaipalikwa bandu bitu baiyi'gane panga makowe manogau, li'nga kwayangatiya apaali mumakowe go imukya. Kwo panga nyo, maisa gabe gaapangali gabule.
\p 
\v 15 Bandu boti bababile nanenga pano bendakusalimia. Tumbwelelo, na wenga kai' wasalimie aumini boti babatupenda muimani.
\p Ngu'ngu' ya Nnu'ngu' ibe pamope na mwenga.
